examples.en: I was uncomfortable about talking to them.
We were in the uncomfortable position of asking for money.
Joe listened, shifting uncomfortably from one foot to another.
Ellen smiled uncomfortably and lowered her gaze.
She lay on the couch, her body uncomfortably twisted.
The silence went on so long that it became very uncomfortable.
Josh felt uncomfortably full, as he was not accustomed to eating so much.
